NAME
    YuiRestClient - Perl module to interact with YaST applications via
    libyui-rest-api.

DESCRIPTION
    See documentation of the [libyui-rest-api
    project](https://github.com/libyui/libyui/tree/master/libyui-rest-api/do
    c) for more details about server side implementation.

VERSION
    This document describes YuiRestClient version 0.1.

SYNOPSIS
      use YuiRestClient;
      use constant API_VERSION => 'v1';

      my $app = YuiRestClient::App->new({
              port        => $port,
              host        => $host,
              api_version => API_VERSION
          });
      $app->check_connection();
      my $btn = $app->button({id => 'btn_ok'});
      $btn->click();

